> This is really dumb. Mailing lists suck, and this one in particular sucks a
> lot because it's too damn big to be a mailing list. It really needs to be a
> newsgroup. With a mailing list, every single article comes to my account even
> though I'm only interested in 1/10 of them. With a newsgroup, I scan the
> subject lines and select the ones I want, and the bulk of the rest of them
